---
title: Tandoori-Style Grilled Chicken Breasts with Garlic Naan and Masala Potatoes
description: Tender chicken gets a quick marinade in aromatic Indian spices, before grilling to adds flavour reminiscent of a blazing hot tandoor oven. Golden naan with garlic butter completes this delicious meal!
